edu.ncsu.csc216.garage.model.dealer

Class ServiceManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.ncsu.csc216.garage.model.dealer.ServiceManager
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Manageable

    public class ServiceManager
extends java.lang.Object
implements Manageable
    Class defines state and behavior for a ServiceManager object that acts as the single entry point of the GUI into the back-end model of the program. ServiceManager oversees and manipulates a Garage list of ServiceBays as well as a VehicleList of Vehicles awaiting service.
    Author:
    Nick Garner
